  taskName: primordial molecule
  taskType: 0
  difficulty: 0
  rawText: In de beninging, da world was, like, not there. But then, suddenly, it
    was. And that was crazy. Crazy? I was crazy once, but that came later in the
    timeline. At this moment, I was molecules. Just moving thu space and stuff. Anyway,
    Things were pretty chill. A bunch of us molecules felt like making a big sphere,
    so we did. Then some of the molecules were like, "wouldn't be neat if we were,
    like, alive?" n' some of the other guys were like, "yea, I guess." So we just
    be chillin' in the primordial soup for however long we were there, but then some
    other guy was like, "I'm outta here." Luckily, the sphere, which called Earth
    or something, seemed to cool down a bit, and apparently there was an ozone and
    everything. There might've been food up there, according to him, so I figured
    I might as well go check it out. So now I'm just chillin' on the beach, think
    I might get legs later, idk.
